4
00:02:36,487 --> 00:02:39,479
Kuda ides, brate?

5
00:02:39,687 --> 00:02:44,283
Nisam znao da imam brata.

6
00:02:47,287 --> 00:02:50,279
Gde ja idem? Ko bi to znao?

7
00:02:51,287 --> 00:02:55,678
Ti si stranac.
Ja ti mogu pokazati put.

8
00:02:55,887 --> 00:02:57,878
Sta?

9
00:02:58,087 --> 00:03:03,081
Bozji ce ti pokazati put,
siguran sam u to.

10
00:03:03,287 --> 00:03:07,280
Moram da te zamolim za veliku uslugu,
veoma blisku mome srcu.

11
00:03:08,687 --> 00:03:13,317
- Od mene trazis uslugu?
- Naravno.

12
00:03:13,527 --> 00:03:16,519
Znam da si vredan nje.

13
00:03:21,287 --> 00:03:23,084
Bice mi zadovoljstvo.

14
00:03:25,287 --> 00:03:30,281
Nemoj se uvrediti,
ako govorim sa tobom veoma otvoreno.

15
00:03:30,487 --> 00:03:35,038
Ne mogu da ne primetim
da si u ovom trenutku u problemima.

16
00:03:35,247 --> 00:03:38,717
Treba ti novac.

17
00:03:40,247 --> 00:03:46,277
Nemoj da mislis da te vredjam,
moze se desiti bilo kome.

18
00:03:48,287 --> 00:03:53,839
Sad, ja imam mnogo vise novca
nego sto mi je potrebno.

19
00:03:54,047 --> 00:03:56,481
Molim te...

20
00:03:56,687 --> 00:04:03,286
Hoces li mi reci koliko ti je potrebno
bar za najprece potrebe.

21
00:04:03,487 --> 00:04:09,005
- 20 franaka ne bi bilo lose.
- Trebace ti vise od toga.

22
00:04:09,207 --> 00:04:13,280
- Trebace ti barem 200.
- 200 franaka?

23
00:04:13,487 --> 00:04:16,877
Naravno, 200 franaka bi bilo mnogo bolje.

24
00:04:17,887 --> 00:04:20,879
- Ne mogu da prihvatim.
- Zasto ne?

25
00:04:23,287 --> 00:04:26,882
Zato sto ne bih znao kako
da vratim toliko novca.

26
00:04:27,087 --> 00:04:30,284
Mozes da se vratis da mi trazis nazad.

27
00:04:30,487 --> 00:04:34,878
Ja nemam kucu,
spavam ispod mostova.

28
00:04:35,087 --> 00:04:38,079
Svake noci drugi most.

29
00:04:39,927 --> 00:04:45,126
Ali ja sam covek od casti,
znam kako da se ponasam.

30
00:04:45,327 --> 00:04:49,286
Ja jednostavno nemam adresu,
to je sve.

31
00:04:49,487 --> 00:04:55,005
Ja takodje nemam adresu,
ne bih mogao ni da ti kazem ime banke.

32
00:04:55,207 --> 00:04:59,200
Prihvati moj novac i ne brini.

33
00:04:59,407 --> 00:05:05,516
To je bezvezna suma novca
za coveka kao sto si ti.

34
00:05:05,727 --> 00:05:08,719
Ja znam da si ti castan covek.

35
00:05:08,927 --> 00:05:15,924
Ako nekad budes u mogucnosti da mi otplatis dug,
mozes da mi ucinis uslugu za koju sam te pitao.

36
00:05:16,127 --> 00:05:20,598
Moram da ti poverim nesto...

37
00:05:20,807 --> 00:05:23,799
...veoma neobicno.

38
00:05:24,007 --> 00:05:29,286
Citao sam pricu
o maloj Terezi...

39
00:05:29,487 --> 00:05:32,479
...svetici Lizijea.

40
00:05:32,687 --> 00:05:37,078
I nakon toga dozivljavao sam cuda...

41
00:05:37,287 --> 00:05:41,075
...cuda preobracanja.

42
00:05:41,287 --> 00:05:45,997
Zbog toga sam odlucio
da zivim zivot siromaha...

43
00:05:46,207 --> 00:05:52,680
...da zivim kao ljudi,
koji dolaze da spavaju ispod mostova.

44
00:05:52,887 --> 00:05:58,883
Veoma sam posvecen
toj statui male Tereze.

45
00:05:59,087 --> 00:06:03,683
Nalazi se u crkvi
Santa Marije de Batinjon...

46
00:06:03,887 --> 00:06:08,915
...ne mozes je promasiti, u glavnoj je
ulici pored zida. - Ali ja...

47
00:06:09,127 --> 00:06:12,278
Ne brini.

48
00:06:12,487 --> 00:06:18,483
Ako budes u poziciji
da vratis novac...

49
00:06:18,687 --> 00:06:24,683
tj. ako ti savest dozvoli
da ostanes duznik...

50
00:06:24,887 --> 00:06:29,483
...onda uzmi novac i predaj ga
svesteniku na kraju mise.

51
00:06:29,687 --> 00:06:36,081
Ako postoji neko kome treba
da budes duznik, od sada...

52
00:06:36,287 --> 00:06:39,006
...onda je to mala Tereza.

53
00:06:40,687 --> 00:06:43,679
Zato, ne zaboravi.

54
00:06:45,087 --> 00:06:48,875
Ne zaboravi adresu svetice.

55
00:06:49,887 --> 00:06:51,878
Hvala ti.

56
00:06:53,007 --> 00:06:59,003
Dajem ti obecanje.
Odrzacu svoju rec.

57
00:07:00,087 --> 00:07:05,081
- Mislim da je najbolje da to uradim
u nedelju, zar ne? - Bilo bi savrseno.

58
00:07:09,687 --> 00:07:12,155
Bilo mi je veliko zadovoljstvo.

59
00:10:06,887 --> 00:10:09,879
"Tereza."

60
00:10:12,887 --> 00:10:15,845
"Santa Marija..."

61
00:10:16,047 --> 00:10:21,041
"...de Batinjon"

62
00:10:45,327 --> 00:10:47,477
Supu!

63
00:13:08,767 --> 00:13:11,361
Tvoje stvari.

64
00:15:19,687 --> 00:15:23,680
- Cetvrtak! 
- Vec.

65
00:15:25,767 --> 00:15:30,887
- Rodjen sam u cetvrtak.
- Onda, dobar cetvrtak. - I vama takodje.

66
00:15:50,887 --> 00:15:53,082
Kafu, molim.

67
00:15:58,087 --> 00:16:02,080
- Izvinite, rum.
- Ne sluzimo alkohol.

68
00:17:08,487 --> 00:17:10,682
Dobar dan.

69
00:17:12,087 --> 00:17:14,078
Momenat.

70
00:17:15,687 --> 00:17:18,076
Odmah se vracam.

71
00:19:05,487 --> 00:19:08,479
Kafu i rum, molim.

72
00:19:30,287 --> 00:19:32,278
12 franaka.

73
00:19:58,767 --> 00:20:04,364
Da li vas zanima posao?
Sutra moram da se selim.

74
00:20:04,567 --> 00:20:07,559
Mozes da zaradis malo.

75
00:20:08,687 --> 00:20:16,275
Vec sam zvao par ljudi,
ali moja zena je nestabilna.

76
00:20:16,487 --> 00:20:22,756
Boji se da oni nece uspeti.
Ja imam posla oko radnje.

77
00:20:22,967 --> 00:20:25,959
Da li bi mogao da nam pomognes?

78
00:20:27,687 --> 00:20:31,077
- Naravno.
- Trajalo bi dva dana.

79
00:20:31,287 --> 00:20:34,643
- Dva dana?
- Sutra i u subotu.

80
00:20:38,887 --> 00:20:41,196
U redu je, odgovara.

81
00:20:50,087 --> 00:20:54,683
- Dvesta franaka je u redu?
- Da, lepo od vas.

82
00:20:54,887 --> 00:20:57,879
Slazete li se?

83
00:20:58,087 --> 00:21:01,079
- Savrseno je.
- Onda, pijmo za to.

84
00:21:02,487 --> 00:21:04,682
Na moj racun.

85
00:21:04,887 --> 00:21:08,675
Zato sto je danas zaista dobar dan.

86
00:21:08,887 --> 00:21:10,878
Cetvrtak je.

87
00:21:12,287 --> 00:21:16,280
- Danas mi je rodjendan.
- Zaista?

88
00:21:18,287 --> 00:21:20,278
Manje - vise.

89
00:21:31,687 --> 00:21:34,918
Sledece je na moj racun.
To je pitanje casti.

90
00:21:38,287 --> 00:21:42,280
Pogledajte u moje ruke,
i one ce vam reci...

91
00:21:42,487 --> 00:21:45,797
...ali ja sam takodje i dzentlmen.
- Verujem.

92
00:21:47,247 --> 00:21:50,762
Ovo je moja vizit karta u radnji.

93
00:21:50,967 --> 00:21:53,606
Napisacu adresu ovde.

94
00:22:07,287 --> 00:22:11,724
- Sta to radite?
- Moj je red, dogovorili smo se.

95
00:22:19,887 --> 00:22:24,677
Uzmite ovo kao avans,
kako bi sutra dosli zasigurno.

96
00:22:24,887 --> 00:22:29,119
Kada posao bude zavrsen,
dacu vam ostatak...

97
00:22:29,327 --> 00:22:31,363
...i nazdravicemo ponovo.

98
00:22:33,687 --> 00:22:37,077
Ali sada, moj prijatelju,
ja moram da krenem.

99
00:22:47,487 --> 00:22:51,685
Ne zaboravi. Sutra...

100
00:22:51,887 --> 00:22:54,276
... u osam sati.

101
00:22:54,487 --> 00:22:57,923
- Osam sati.
- Dovidjenja, prijatelju.

102
00:23:50,487 --> 00:23:52,682
Ja...

103
00:23:52,887 --> 00:23:56,402
- Hteo bih novcanik.
- Novcanik?

104
00:23:58,607 --> 00:24:01,121
Mozda imamo nesto za vas.

105
00:24:26,487 --> 00:24:28,557
Ovi su skoro novi.

106
00:24:28,767 --> 00:24:34,285
Klijenti su ih menjali za kapris.
Ovo su skoriji modeli.

107
00:24:34,487 --> 00:24:37,479
Ovi kostaju mnogo manje.

108
00:24:37,687 --> 00:24:40,679
- Shvatam.
- Dopada vam se taj?

109
00:24:41,687 --> 00:24:43,678
Veoma je lep.

110
00:24:57,207 --> 00:24:59,198
Dovidjenja.

111
00:28:12,887 --> 00:28:16,880
Dobro jutro, madam.
- Pocnite od kuhinje.

112
00:28:23,687 --> 00:28:28,636
Ja sam ovde zbog...
- Dobar dan, podjite za mnom.

113
00:28:39,527 --> 00:28:42,678
Moj suprug mi je rekao
da mogu da vam verujem.

114
00:28:42,887 --> 00:28:46,641
Za delikatnije stvari
koristicemo novine.

115
00:28:46,847 --> 00:28:48,883
- Znate li kako?
- Da.

116
00:28:50,167 --> 00:28:53,682
Prepustite meni.
Uradicu sve sto treba.

117
00:28:53,887 --> 00:28:57,766
- Cime se bavite?
- Bio sam rudar...

118
00:28:58,887 --> 00:29:03,677
...kao i moj otac
a pre toga i moj deda.

119
00:29:17,487 --> 00:29:19,478
Delikatno.

120
00:29:38,767 --> 00:29:41,918
Izvolite, ovo je za vas.

121
00:29:42,127 --> 00:29:46,120
- Vidimo se ponovo u sedam sati.
- Sedam sati.

122
00:29:49,887 --> 00:29:54,722
- Sutra, po dogovoru.
- Ne trosite novac na pice.

123
00:30:35,287 --> 00:30:39,678
Dobro je, niste sve potrosili na pice.
Udjite.

124
00:30:39,887 --> 00:30:41,878
Da, madam.

125
00:31:47,487 --> 00:31:49,478
Dovidjenja.

126
00:31:50,687 --> 00:31:55,283
- Ekoci je ovde.
I sto je postavljen!

127
00:31:55,487 --> 00:31:58,479
Zbogom, prijatelju.

128
00:32:03,287 --> 00:32:05,278
Srecno.

129
00:32:27,687 --> 00:32:30,679
- Danas je subota, zar ne?
- Tako je.

130
00:32:35,887 --> 00:32:38,321
Znaci, sutra je nedelja.

131
00:32:38,527 --> 00:32:43,078
"Dug, 200 franaka."

132
00:32:43,287 --> 00:32:46,757
"Ostatak, 100 franaka."

133
00:32:48,687 --> 00:32:53,078
"100 franaka."

134
00:33:18,887 --> 00:33:21,879
Gospodine! Vas kaput.

135
00:33:24,687 --> 00:33:26,678
Hvala.

136
00:34:32,767 --> 00:34:34,678
Da!

137
00:34:47,287 --> 00:34:49,278
Tereza!

138
00:35:10,887 --> 00:35:13,879
Uradite kako treba!

139
00:35:19,487 --> 00:35:21,478
Gde je crkva?

140
00:35:33,687 --> 00:35:35,678
Crkva?

141
00:35:37,887 --> 00:35:39,878
Hvala.

142
00:35:46,887 --> 00:35:49,879
- Misa je zavrsena.
- Jeste.

143
00:35:51,687 --> 00:35:54,679
- Kada je sledeca misa?
- U podne.

144
00:37:03,407 --> 00:37:06,365
Dajte mi jos jedno pice.

145
00:37:06,567 --> 00:37:09,559
Imajuci u vidu da moram da cekam...

146
00:37:28,287 --> 00:37:30,278
Cekate li nekog?

147
00:37:31,287 --> 00:37:34,279
Cekam da pocne misa.

148
00:38:46,687 --> 00:38:48,678
Pocela je.

149
00:38:48,887 --> 00:38:50,878
Sta?

150
00:38:51,087 --> 00:38:54,318
Misa.
Niste li cekali zbog mise?

151
00:38:59,487 --> 00:39:01,478
Tako je!

152
00:39:04,287 --> 00:39:07,757
Imam zakazano.
Veoma je bitno!

153
00:39:16,287 --> 00:39:18,278
Andreas!

154
00:39:23,927 --> 00:39:25,918
Andreas!

155
00:40:15,007 --> 00:40:16,998
Andreas.

156
00:40:23,687 --> 00:40:25,678
Jesi li sam?

157
00:40:28,287 --> 00:40:30,642
Jesam.

158
00:40:31,487 --> 00:40:35,162
Kreni sa mnom.
Ili ides negde?

159
00:40:38,887 --> 00:40:41,640
Imam zakazano.

160
00:40:44,287 --> 00:40:46,926
Sa zenom?

161
00:40:47,767 --> 00:40:49,758
Tereza!

162
00:40:50,887 --> 00:40:53,879
Je li ona vaznija od mene?

163
00:40:59,687 --> 00:41:02,076
Podji sa mnom, treba da razgovaramo.

164
00:43:11,887 --> 00:43:14,879
Da li ti se dopada ovo mesto?

165
00:43:15,687 --> 00:43:17,678
Meni veoma znaci.

166
00:43:39,847 --> 00:43:45,046
Mogu li da narucim i za tebe?
Ako mi jos uvek verujes.

167
00:44:03,287 --> 00:44:04,766
Izvinite, gospodine.

168
00:44:20,487 --> 00:44:26,881
Umirem od zelje da cujem o tebi.
Gde si bio, sta si radio...

169
00:44:32,687 --> 00:44:34,678
Sta radis sada?

170
00:44:35,887 --> 00:44:38,720
Poceo sam da radim ponovo.

171
00:44:42,407 --> 00:44:44,398
Radio sam dva dana.

172
00:44:46,887 --> 00:44:50,084
Pijem, spavam ispod mosta...

173
00:44:52,887 --> 00:44:54,878
Sta je sa tobom?

174
00:44:56,687 --> 00:44:59,804
Verovatno si dobro provela vreme.

175
00:45:37,287 --> 00:45:39,278
Sta je sa Terezom?

176
00:45:40,687 --> 00:45:45,681
Da se nisam pojavila na vreme,
ti bi sada bio sa njom.

177
00:45:52,447 --> 00:45:54,438
Da.

178
00:45:59,487 --> 00:46:01,478
Da.

179
00:48:18,487 --> 00:48:20,603
Mogu li da naplatim, molim.

180
00:48:26,887 --> 00:48:30,880
- Ne, ja sam zvala.
- Gospodin je trazio racun.

181
00:48:57,887 --> 00:48:59,878
Znaci, bogat si.

182
00:49:03,287 --> 00:49:05,278
Da.

183
00:49:06,287 --> 00:49:12,283
Poslednjih par dana
zaista sam poceo da verujem u cuda.

184
00:49:16,287 --> 00:49:18,596
Da li ti verujes u cuda?

185
00:49:44,287 --> 00:49:46,278
Nisam rodjen za ovo!

186
00:49:47,687 --> 00:49:50,838
Zar nisi probao, od onda?

187
00:50:55,487 --> 00:50:58,877
Oduvek sam volela da igram!

188
00:53:08,887 --> 00:53:10,878
Udji.

189
00:56:57,287 --> 00:56:59,278
Gospodine!

190
00:57:00,287 --> 00:57:02,278
Gospodine!

191
00:57:02,487 --> 00:57:04,478
Zatvaramo.

192
00:58:45,367 --> 00:58:49,076
Zasto nisi dosao
da me vidis u nedelju?

193
00:58:58,687 --> 00:59:02,077
Kako to razgovaras sa mnom?

194
00:59:03,087 --> 00:59:07,285
- Zar ne znas da sam ti ja otac.
- Oprosti mi oce.

195
00:59:07,487 --> 00:59:11,480
Ali, ucini mi uslugu.
U nedelju ujutru dodji kod mene...

196
00:59:11,687 --> 00:59:15,282
...u crkvu Santa Marije de Batinjol.

197
00:59:16,287 --> 00:59:18,562
Tereza!

198
00:59:24,087 --> 00:59:26,681
Oprosti mi!

199
00:59:30,087 --> 00:59:32,476
Mislio sam da sanjam.

200
00:59:32,687 --> 00:59:36,680
Mislio sam da imam devojcicu
kao sto si ti.

